      "review_summary": "The PR adds a shared Allow Always unavailable-reason helper, uses it in exec approval reply and forwarder messages, and adds reply-renderer tests for one-shot and missing-ask cases.\n\nPR surface: Source +30, Tests +27. Total +57 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows current main collapses ask=always and one-shot persistence into the same allowedDecisions shape, while the foreground approval message still prints policy-only copy whenever Allow Always is absent; Mantis also captured a visible before/after prompt for the PR's reply path.",
